        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "If you're wondering, that's often a sign to ask. Common concerns include not speaking as much as peers, difficulty being understood, frustration when communicating, or not responding to their name. A free consultation can help us figure it out together."
        }
